cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServErrDrops.description: This object represents the number of times a DHCP proxy server control message is dropped by the Gateway due to some error in the message.

cgprsAccPtActiveBearers.name: cgprsAccPtActiveBearers
cgprsAccPtActiveBearers.description: This object indicates the current number of active Bearer on this APN.

cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServTxErrDrops.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServTxErrDrops
cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServTxErrDrops.description: This object represents the number of times an outgoing DHCP proxy server control message is dropped by the Gateway due to some failure in the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServIpAllocErr.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServIpAllocErr
cgprsAccPtDhcpProxServIpAllocErr.description: This object represents the number of times an incoming DHCP proxy server control message has been dropped by the Gateway due to IP allocation error in the message.

cgprsAccPtDedBearerDeactivations.name: cgprsAccPtDedBearerDeactivations
cgprsAccPtDedBearerDeactivations.description: This object represents the total number dedicated bearer deactivation request initiated by the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDedBearerQosUpdate.name: cgprsAccPtDedBearerQosUpdate
cgprsAccPtDedBearerQosUpdate.description: This object represents the total number of dedicated bearer modification request with QoS change initiated by the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDedBearerSucQosUpdate.name: cgprsAccPtDedBearerSucQosUpdate
cgprsAccPtDedBearerSucQosUpdate.description: This object represents the total number of successful dedicated bearer modification request with QoS change initiated by the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDedBearerNoQosUpdate.name: cgprsAccPtDedBearerNoQosUpdate
cgprsAccPtDedBearerNoQosUpdate.description: This object represents the total number of dedicated bearer modification request without QoS change initiated by the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDedBearerSucNoQosUpdate.name: cgprsAccPtDedBearerSucNoQosUpdate
cgprsAccPtDedBearerSucNoQosUpdate.description: This object represents the total number of successful dedicated bearer modification request without QoS change initiated by the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtIpv4v6MsActivatedDynamicPdps.name: cgprsAccPtIpv4v6MsActivatedDynamicPdps
cgprsAccPtIpv4v6MsActivatedDynamicPdps.description: This object indicates the total number of IPv4v6 PDP or Bearer context activation procedures initiated by any MS on this APN.

cgprsAccPtIpv4v6MsSuccActivatedDynamicPd.name: cgprsAccPtIpv4v6MsSuccActivatedDynamicPdps
cgprsAccPtIpv4v6MsSuccActivatedDynamicPd.description: This object indicates the total number of successfully completed IPv4v6 PDP or Bearer context activation procedures initiated by MS on this APN.

cgprsAccPtFailMsActivatedPdps.name: cgprsAccPtFailMsActivatedPdps
cgprsAccPtFailMsActivatedPdps.description: This object indicates the total number of failed PDP or Bearer context activation procedures initiated by MS on this APN.

cgprsAccPtFailPdpUpdate.name: cgprsAccPtFailPdpUpdate
cgprsAccPtFailPdpUpdate.description: This object represents the total number of failed PDP or Bearer context update for the initiated update requests on this APN.

cgprsAccPtUpdateRspTimeOut.name: cgprsAccPtUpdateRspTimeOut
cgprsAccPtUpdateRspTimeOut.description: This object represents the total number of failed PDP or Bearer context update response not received due to the time out for the initiated update requests on this APN.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxyStatsTable.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxyStatsTable
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxyStatsTable.description: This table contains the DHCPv6 proxy server performance statistics for each APN on this Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxyStatsEntry.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxyStatsEntry
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxyStatsEntry.description: There is an entry in this table for each APN in the Gateway.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqRcvd.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqRcvd
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqRcvd.description: This object represents the total number of DHCPv6 information request message handled by the Gateway's DHCPv6 proxy-client.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqRply.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqRply
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqRply.description: This object represents the total number of DHCPv6 response message sent by the Gateway's DHCPv6 proxy-client.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqLocRply.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqLocRply
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxInforeqLocRply.description: This object represents the total number of times a local response was sent for the DHCPv6 information request received by the Gateway's DHCPv6 proxy-client.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpAllocSuc.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpAllocSuc
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpAllocSuc.description: This object represents the total number of times DHCPv6 IP allocation was successful.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpAllocFail.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpAllocFail
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpAllocFail.description: This object represents the total number of times DHCPv6 IP allocation was failed.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpRelease.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpRelease
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpRelease.description: This object represents the total number of times an allocated DHCPv6 IP was released.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpRenewFail.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpRenewFail
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxIpRenewFail.description: This object represents the total number of times an allocated DHCPv6 IP renewal was failed.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxUnkwnMsg.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxUnkwnMsg
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxUnkwnMsg.description: This object represents the total number of times an unknown message was handled by the Gateway's DHCPv6 proxy-client.

cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxErrs.name: cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxErrs
cgprsAccPtDhcpv6ProxErrs.description: This object represents the total number of times an error has occurred at the Gateway's DHCPv6 proxy-client.

cgprsAccPtThruputStatsTable.name: cgprsAccPtThruputStatsTable
cgprsAccPtThruputStatsTable.description: This table contains the throughput statistics of each APN on this Gateway.

cgprsAccPtThruputInterval.name: cgprsAccPtThruputInterval
cgprsAccPtThruputInterval.description: This object represents the time interval at which the statistics are sampled. Interval configuration is out of the scope of the MIB and are covered in CISCO-GGSN-MIB.

cgprsAccPtThruPutLastCollected.name: cgprsAccPtThruPutLastCollected
cgprsAccPtThruPutLastCollected.description: This object represents the delta value between the time when this data is collected and the time it is been retrieved.

cgprsAccPtUpstrByteCount.name: cgprsAccPtUpstrByteCount
cgprsAccPtUpstrByteCount.description: This object represents the total payload volume in upstream traffic sent on this APN in the last sampling period specified by cgprsAccPtThruputInterval.

cgprsAccPtDownstrByteCount.name: cgprsAccPtDownstrByteCount
cgprsAccPtDownstrByteCount.description: This object represents the total payload volume in downstream traffic sent on this APN in the last sampling period specified by cgprsAccPtThruputInterval.

cgprsAccPtUpstrPktCount.name: cgprsAccPtUpstrPktCount
cgprsAccPtUpstrPktCount.description: This object represents the number of upstream packets sent on this APN in the last sampling period specified by cgprsAccPtThruputInterval.

cgprsAccPtDownstrPktCount.name: cgprsAccPtDownstrPktCount
cgprsAccPtDownstrPktCount.description: This object represents the number of downstream packets sent on this APN in the last sampling period specified by cgprsAccPtThruputInterval.

cgprsAccPtMsAddrType.name: cgprsAccPtMsAddrType
cgprsAccPtMsAddrType.description: This object specifies the type of Internet address denoted by cgprsAccPtMsAllocAddr, cgprsAccPtMsNewAddr and cgprsAccPtMsTpduDstAddr.

cgprsAccPtMsAllocAddr.name: cgprsAccPtMsAllocAddr
cgprsAccPtMsAllocAddr.description: This object specifies the IP address that is assigned to the MS during PDP activation.

cgprsAccPtMsNewAddr.name: cgprsAccPtMsNewAddr
cgprsAccPtMsNewAddr.description: This object specifies the fake IP address that is used by the MS.

cgprsAccPtMsTpduDstAddr.name: cgprsAccPtMsTpduDstAddr
cgprsAccPtMsTpduDstAddr.description: This object specifies the upstream TPDU destination address used by a MS that falls in the reserved range of IP addresses for PLMN devices.

cgprsAccPtCfgNotif.name: cgprsAccPtCfgNotif
cgprsAccPtCfgNotif.description: A notification of this type is generated when an entry is generated in the cgprsAccPtCfgNotifHistTable and cgprsAccPtCfgNotifEnable is set to true.

cgprsAccPtSecSrcViolNotif.name: cgprsAccPtSecSrcViolNotif
cgprsAccPtSecSrcViolNotif.description: A notification of this type is generated when security violation as specified by cgprsAccPtVerifyUpStrTpduSrcAddr occurs on an APN.

cgprsAccPtSecDestViolNotif.name: cgprsAccPtSecDestViolNotif
cgprsAccPtSecDestViolNotif.description: A notification of this type is generated when security violation as specified by cgprsAccPtVerifyUpStrTpduDstAddr occurs on an APN.

cgprsAccPtMaintenanceNotif.name: cgprsAccPtMaintenanceNotif
cgprsAccPtMaintenanceNotif.description: A notification of this type is generated when APN is placed in maintenance mode which is specified by cgprsAccPtOperationMode.

cgprsAccPtInServiceNotif.name: cgprsAccPtInServiceNotif
cgprsAccPtInServiceNotif.description: A notification of this type is generated when APN is placed in in-service mode which is specified by cgprsAccPtOperationMode.
